tafsir[75]{c,v,t}:
  39,1,"Jippagol Alqur'aana, ko immorde ka Allah, FooluЙ—o Mo gooto foolataa, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o e tagu Mun, e toppitagol Mun e sari'a Mun. Wanaa e goЙ—Й—o goo, ko woori Mo, nde jippori."
  39,2,"Men jippinirii Deftere Alqur'aana nden e maaЙ—a, an NulaaЙ—o, e hoore goonga. Kumpite mayre fow ko goonga, Гұaawooje mayre fow kadi ko nunЙ—uЙ—e. Haray rewu Allah, wootinЙ—inaa mo, laЙ“Й“inanaa Mo tawhiidi e hoore sirku."
  39,3,"Anndee, ko Allah woodani, diina laaЙ“uka e sirku kan. ЖҒen non Й“e Й“eya jogitori yiЙ—Й“e gaanin Allah, immorde e sanamuuji e bewinayЙ—i, Й—i Й“e rewata Й“e acca Allah, Й“e wona e ngantinorgol Й—um, wiide: Men rewiraali Й—ii, si wanaa tun no Й“adinira men ka Allah, martaba, Й—i hewtina Mo haajuuji amen, Й—i tefana men ka Makko. Pellet, Allah Гұaawoyay hakkunde gomЙ—imЙ“e wootimЙ“e Mo Й“en, e yedduЙ“e sirkuЙ“e Й“en, Г‘alnde Darngal, e kon ko Й“e luutondiraynoo e mun, ka tawhiidi. Pellet, Allah fewnataa e goonga, on fenoowo dammba e Alla sirku, dullanoowo neemaaji Allah Й—in e makko."
  39,4,"Sinno Allah yiЙ—uo siforgol Й“iЙ—Й—o, O suЙ“otono ko O yiЙ—i, e tagu Makko ngun, O waЙ—a on Й—on Й“iЙ—Й—o Makko. Kono O senike O laaЙ“ii e kon ko sirkooЙ“e Й“en wowolata ! Ko Kanko woni Allah Gooto On ka jaati, e ka sijaafi e ka golle Makko. KafidiiЙ—o alanaa Mo e Й—in. Ko O FooluЙ—o tagu Makko ngun fow."
  39,5,"O tagirii kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, ГұenЖҙal yottiingal, ko fijindaaru alaa e mu'un, wano tooГұuЙ“e Й“en aaЖҙorta. Himo suddira jemma on, Гұalawma on, O suddira kadi Гұalorma on, jemma on. O elti naange ngen e lewru ndun, tawi kala majji, hino doga haa e happu eЙ“Й“aaЙ—o, on woni lannugol Й—am nguurndam. Haray anndee, ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o, yoftotoowo ayЙ“e Mun, Mo gooto foolataa, Haforoowo junuubi kala tuubuЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en."
  39,6,"Joomi mon, onon Й“ee yimЙ“e, tagii on e fittaandu wooturu, ndun woni Aadama. Refti O tagi e makko, genndo makko on Hawaa. O tagani on gelooЙ—i e na'i e dammi e be'i, nooneeji jeetati, noone kala, gorel e deyel. Himo tagira on ka teege yumma mon en, sagara naЙ“i sagara, e nder niЙ“e reedu e rennga e jowtol. Ko On mooЙ—on tagoowo Й—um fow, woni Allah, Joomi mon. Ko Kanko laamu woodani. ReweteeЙ—o e goonga alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Ko honno ferlitoraЙ—on e rewugol ko tagataa, acca Й—on tagoowo On?"
  39,7,"Si onon Й“ee yimЙ“e, on yeddii Joomi mon, anndon tun, Allah ko yondiniiЙ—o e gomЙ—inal mon, keeferaaku mon, lorrataa Mo. Ko onon Й—um lorrata, tawde Allah kan, O siforaali yamiroowo pankere e ko aГұinii. Si on yettii Mo non e neemaaji Makko Й—in, on gomЙ—inii Mo, O weltanto on, O warjoo on e Й—um. Anndon wonii bakkondinki woo, ronndantaako wokki goo. Kala e ko faggitanii hoore mun. Refti ko ka Joomi mon tun, woni ruttorde mon, Г‘alnde Darngal; O yeetitoo on, fii ko gollaynoЙ—on aduna, O yoЙ“ita on, njoЙ“di golle mon Й—en. Kanko seniiЙ—o On, pellet, ko O annduЙ—o ko woni e Й“erЙ—e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Huunde e ko woni e majje, suuЙ—aaki Mo."
  39,8,"Si lorra heЙ“ii yedduЙ—o, wono Гұawu maa sattireede arsike maa hulugol yoolaade, o toroo nde Joomi makko hunciranta mo Й—um, ruttagol e Makko, Kanko tun. Refti non, si Allah neeminirii mo huncangol mo on lorra, o yejjita fii Allah, Mo O torotonoo On, ado Й—um. O waЙ—ana Mo kafidiiЙ—i, reweteeЙ—i, ko wanaa Allah, no o majjinira woЙ—Й“e goo, e laawol Allah ngol. NulaaЙ—o, maakan sugu on Й—on : dakmitor yeddugol maa ngol, yeru ko o heddoriЙ—aa e duuЙ“i kon. Anndaa pellet, ko a jeyaaЙ—o e yimЙ“e duumoytooЙ“e ka Yiite Й“en, Г‘alnde Darngal."
  39,9,"Kaa ko on Й—oftiiЙ—o Allah, feЖҙЖҙiniroowo jemma on, sujjangol Mo, darorana Mo naafe, hara himo huli lepte laakara Й—en, himo jortrii yurmeende Joomi makko nden, kaa ko yedduЙ—o rewoowo Allah on ka saЙ—teende tun, o yedda Mo ka hoyeende, o waЙ—ana Mo kafidiiЙ—i? An NulaaЙ—o, maaku : Hara Й“en annduЙ“e ko Allah farli kon e maЙ“Й“e, hino fota e Й“en Й“e anndaa huunde e Й—um? Anndu ko taskotoo kon ko senndi Й—in feddeeji Й—iЙ—i, ko joomiraaЙ“e haqqille hisuЙ—e Й—en."
  39,10,"An NulaaЙ—o, maakan jeyaaЙ“e Am gomЙ—imЙ“e Lam Min e NulaaЙ“e Am Й“en: huliree Joomi mon, Й—oftagol yamaruyeeji Makko, e woЙ—Й—itagol haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko. Hino woodani moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e golle Й“en e mon aduna, moЖҙЖҙoreede e mun aduna, walleede e cellal e jawdi, ka laakara, hara ko Aljanna. Leydi Allah ndin ko yaajundi, feree e mayri, haa e nokku ka waawoton rewude Mo woo, ka goЙ—Й—o haЙ—ataa on Й—um. Anndon muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en, Й“e timminirante njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin Г‘alnde Darngal, ko aldaa e limaneede maa etaneede, Й—uuЙ—i fanЙ—i."
  39,11,"An NulaaЙ—o, maaku: min mi yamiraama rewugol Allah tun, mi laЙ“Й“inana Mo dewal ngal."
  39,12,"O yamirimmi kadi, wonugol arano e jebbilaniiЙ“e Mo Й“en, yankinaniiЙ“e Mo e Й—ee mofte."
  39,13,"An NulaaЙ—o, maaku: min miЙ—o huli, si mi yeddii Allah, mi Й—oftaaki Mo, nde lepte Г‘alaande Mawnde nden heЙ“atammi, nden woni Г‘alnde Darngal."
  39,14,"An NulaaЙ—o, maaku : min ko Allah tun mi rewata, mi laЙ“Й“inana Mo dewal. Wanaa goЙ—Й—o goo, mi waЙ—anta Й—um."
  39,15,"Onon sirkooЙ“e Й“en non, rewee ko yiЙ—uЙ—on e sanamu, hara wanaa Kanko. ЖҠum ko kammbaa ! An NulaaЙ—o, maaku: ko woni hayruЙ“e Й“en tigiri, ko Й“en tawata Й“e hayrinii ko'e maЙ“Й“e e Й“eynguureeji maЙ“Й“e, Й“e ronkoya yiidoyde e maЙ“Й“e, si Й“en naatoyii Aljanna, maa Й“e naatidoya e maЙ“Й“e ka Yiite, tawa Й“e yiitidataa poomaa. Anndee ko Й—um tigiri, woni hayrere Й“anngunde nden, ko sikke alaa e mu'un."
  39,16,"Curki e kippoodi wulndi, hino woodirani Й“e senngo dow maЙ“Й“e, e senngo ley maЙ“Й“e. Ko Й—ee lepte jantaaЙ—e fii mun, woni ko Allah hulЙ“irnirta jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Ko onon yo jeyaЙ“Й“e Am, kori huliree Lam, Й—oftagol yamiraaЙ—i Am, woЙ—Й—itoo haЙ—aaЙ—i Am."
  39,17,"ЖҒen woЙ—Й—itiiЙ“e e rewugol sanamuuji Й—in, e kala ko wonaa Allah, Й“e tuubi Й“e ruttii ka Allah, welo-welo Aljanna no woodani Й“e, tuma Й“e maayata, e ka genaale, e Г‘alnde Darngal. An NulaaЙ—o, wewlinir jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en."
  39,18,"ЖҒen nanooЙ“e Konngol Й“en, Й“e senndindira ko moЖҙЖҙi e ko boni e maggol, Й“e jokka ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e maggol. Ko Й“en siforiiЙ“e Й—in sifaaji, woni Й“e Allah fewniri peewal Й“en, ko Й“en woni joomiraaЙ“e haqqille hisuЙ—e Й“en."
  39,19,"Kala mo konngol lepte jojjiri e mun, sabu duumagol mo e yeddugol e majjere, a alanaa on feere, an NulaaЙ—o, fii no feewira. E ko an NulaaЙ—o, waawata daЙ—ndude wa'uЙ—o non e Yiite ngen?"
  39,20,"Si ko Й“en hulirЙ“e Joomi mun, Й—oftagol yamiraaЙ—i Makko, woЙ—Й—itoo haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko, hino woodani Й“e kuЙ“eeje toowuЙ—e fawondiri ka Aljanna, hara canЙ—i no ila senngo ley majje. Ko Allah fodi Й“e Й—um! Allah non firtataa fodoore Makko."
  39,21,"HiЙ—on anndiri seedagol mon, wonnde Allah saaЖҙinirii ndiyam ka kammu, O naadi Й—am e Й“ulli e canЙ—; refi O yaltinira Й—am ndiyam, remuru seedudnu noone, refti O yoorna ndu, yi'aandu an seeditiiЙ—o on, hindu soyЙ—i, Й“aawo ndu wonunoo haako; refti O waЙ—a Й—um ko muncitaa. Pellet, wonii e ko jantaa koo, waaju, wonannde joomiraaЙ“e haqqille Й“en hisuЙ—e Й—en."
  39,22,"E ko on mo Allah yaГұГұani Й“ernde mun fii lislaamu, o feewi e mun, hara himo e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi makko, wa'ata wa yoora Й“enrdeejo e jantagol Allah? ЖҒe fotataa fes. Tawde ko feewuЙ“e Й“en, daЙ—ata, yoora Й“erЙ—e'en e jantagol Allah .ЖҒen wonii e majjere Й“anngunde."
  39,23,"Allah jppinii e NulaaЙ—o Makko on Muhammadu (yo o his) Alqur'aana, Й“urnde moЖҙЖҙude yewtere. O waЙ—i nden nanndude ka goonga, e ka moЖҙЖҙugol, e ka yuЙ“Й“ondirgol e waasde luutondirde. Fillayeeji e Гұaawooje hino Й—uuЙ—i e mayre, kaГұum e fodooje e kammbaa, e sifaaji yimЙ“e goonga, e yimЙ“e meere Й“en ekn. Guri Й“en hulooЙ“e Joomi mun, hino riЙ“ira sabu nanugol kammbaaji ko woni e mayre, refti guri e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e deeЖҙira jantagol Innde Allah, tuma Й“e nani jortagol e welo-welo ko woni e mayre. Koo ko jantaa e ko Alqur'aana battinta, ko peewal Allah, ngal O fewnirta mo O muuyani, O hoyna mo Mo O muuyani. Kala non mo Allah fewnaali, haray fewnoowo mo alaa."
  39,24,"Kere on mo Allah fewni aduna, O naadoya mo Aljanna laakara, on fotay wa yedduЙ—o maayi e keeferaaku on, naatoyoowo Yiite, tonnge juuЙ—e e koyЙ—e, mo tawata waawoytaa daЙ—irde Yiite ngen, si wanaa tun o fewtinira nge yeeso makko ngon? TooГұuЙ“e Й“en feliree wi'aneede ontuma: meeЙ—en non hannde, kon ko wonunoЙ—on faggitorde geddi e keeferaaku. Ko njoЙ“di mon ndin nii."
  39,25,"Mofte adinooЙ“e Й“ee sirkooЙ“e, kadi fennuno NulaaЙ“e mun, lepte Й—en ardirani Й“e juhal, fewndo ka Й“e so'aa-anndude, sakko Й“e hebiloranaЙ—e tuubugol."
  39,26,"Allah meeЙ—iriЙ“e sabu Й—um, lepte koyeera, e jaasere, e wirtere ka ngurrndam aduna. Pellet, ko lepte laakara Й—en habbitiiЙ—e Й“e, Й“uri mawnude e tiiЙ—e, si tawno hiЙ“e anndunoo."
  39,27,"GomЙ—ii Men piyanii yimЙ“e Й“en, e ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinaande e Muhammadu (yo o his) noone kala e mise moЖҙЖҙere e bone, goonga e meere, gomЙ—inal e keeferaaku, ekn. ЖҠum fow, ko jortagol nde Й“e waajitora, Й“e huutora goonga kan, Й“e sela meere nden."
  39,28,"Men waЙ—i nde Alqur'aanaare, janngeteende e haala Aarabu, nde aldaa e ooГұaare maa jiЙ“i-liЙ“i, jortagol no Й“e hulira Allah, jokkugol yamiraaЙ—i Makko, woЙ—Й—itoo haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko."
  39,29,"Allah waЙ—ii misal hakkunde sirkoowo e wootinЙ—inoowo, woni gorko mo lurruЙ“e hawti : si o weltinii woЙ—Й“e Й“en, Й“eya Й“en monoo, o wona e jiЙ“i-liЙ“i. Oya gorko, ko laaЙ“anЙ—o gorko goo, kanko tun, himo anndi ko deeЖҙinta oya, e ko wallinta mo Й“ernde. ЖҒen worЙ“e Й—iЙ—o, Й“e fotataa e misal. Yettoore woodanii Allah. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e anndaa. Ko waЙ—i si Й“e kafida e Allah, goЙ—Й—um goo."
  39,30,"Pelelt, an NulaaЙ—o, ko a maayoowo, kamЙ“e kadi ko Й“e maayooЙ“e, feere mun alaa."
  39,31,"Refti onon Й“ee yimЙ“e, Г‘alnde Darngal, ko ka Joomi mon yeddondiroyton, e ko pooЙ—ondiraynoЙ—on fii mun, goonguЙ—o on seerta e meerenteejo on."
  39,32,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұude haa hewta on dammbuЙ—o e Allah, ko yahdaani e Makko, wano waЙ—angol Mo kafidiiЙ—o, maa genndo maa Й“iЙ—Й—o. Alaa kadi Й“urЙ—o tooГұde wa on fennuЙ—o wahyu on mo NulaaЙ—o Allah on (yo o his) addi. E wonaa ka Yiite woni jaaЖҙorde yeddude Allah Й“en, Й“e yeddi ko NulaaЙ—o Makko on addi kon? Pellet, ko non woniri, weerde maЙ“Й“e, ko nder ton."
  39,33,"On non arduЙ—o e goonga, ka haala e ka kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, foti ko Annabaajo maa goЙ—Й—o goo, o gomЙ—ini Й—um, o gollitiri. Ko Й“en woni gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en tigiri, Й—oftiiЙ“e yamaruyeeji Joomi mun, woЙ—Й—itiiЙ“e haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko."
  39,34,"Hino woodani dakammeeji duumotooЙ—i, ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e; ko Й—um woni njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e golle Й“en, ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e e jiyaaЙ“e."
  39,35,"Fii no Allah momtirana Й“e, ko Й“uri bonnde e ko Й“e gollaynoo e geddi aduna, tawde Й“e tuubii e mun, Й“e ruttike e Joomi maЙ“Й“e. O yoЙ“itira Й“e njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin, ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e kon ko Й“e gollunoo."
  39,36,"Mbela Allah siforaali yonugol jeyaaЙ—o Makko on Muhammadu (yo o his) ka fiyakuuji makko diina e aduna, O duГұana mo ayЙ“e makko? Pellet, O yonay mo. HiЙ“e hulЙ“inire, an NulaaЙ—o, sabu majjere e Й—aayre maЙ“Й“e, Й—in sanamuuji, Й—i Й“e rewata Й“e acca Allah, wiide Й—i memirte bone. Kala non mo Allah hoyni, O hawrinaani mo fewnude, haray fewnoowo on Й—on, alaa."
  39,37,"Kala non mo Allah hawrindini e peewal, alaa haЙ—tanЙ—o majjinde mo. Mbela Allah siforaaki wonnde FooluЙ—o Mo gooto foolataa, Jom leptugol Й“en heefereЙ“e yedduЙ“e Mo? Ko non woniri, Ko O FooluЙ—o, Jom lepte."
  39,38,"Pellet, si an NulaaЙ—o, a lamndike Й“ee sirkooЙ“e: Ko hommbo tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin? Ma Й“e wi'u: Ko Allah tagi Й—i. Awa maakan Й“e, feГұГұinanaaЙ“e, ronkere reweteeЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in: Yeetee lam fii Й—ii sanamuuji, Й—i rewoton gaanin Allah; si Allah faandanike lorra, hara Й—i waaway ittannde lam on lorra? Maa si O faandanike lam moЖҙЖҙere Makko, taw si Й—i haЙ—tani haЙ—ugol lam nden moЖҙЖҙere Makko? Maakan Й“ee: Allah tun yonii lam, ko e Makko mi fawi kala fiyaaku am, ko e Makko kadi tun, woni ko wakkiltoo Й“en tuuginotoo."
  39,39,"An NulaaЙ—o, maaku: Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, golliree no waalorani on, sirkangol Allah. Min ko no Joomi am yamirimmi non, mi gollirta, woni noddugol e tawhiidi, laЙ“Й“inana Mo dewal. Aray ka anndon, battane laawol kala e me'en."
  39,40,"Aray nde anndon, ko hommbo lepte aduna hoynayЙ—e aroyta e muuЙ—um, lepte duumiiЙ—e jippoyoo e makko Г‘alnde Darngal, hara Й—e taЖҙondirtaa, sakko Й—e lanna."
  39,41,"Men jippinirii Deftere Alqur'aana nden, e maaЙ—a an NulaaЙ—o, fii yimЙ“e Й“en, e hoore goonga, no jertiniraaЙ“e. Kala feewuЙ—o, ko hoore makko o feewani, Allah nafitortaa peewal makko, tawde ko O yondiniiЙ—o e Й—um; kala kadi majjuЙ—o, haray lorra mun on, ko e makko yiltotoo, Й—um lorrataa Allah. A wonaali wakkilaaЙ—o Й“ee, fii daranagol Й“e haa Й“e feewa. Ko yottingol tun, fawi maa e maЙ“Й“e."
  39,42,"Allah hino Жҙettita pittaali Й—in, tuma lajal majji timmata, e Й—in Й—i lajal mun timmaali, fewndo Й—oyngol majji. O jogitii Й—in Й—i O Гұaawani maayde, O accita Й—iya, Й—i O Гұaawani heddagol, haa e dumunna happaaЙ—o ka Makko. Pellet, wonii e ko sifaa koo, maandeeji, wonannde Й“e miijitotooЙ“e, tinndinayЙ—i, wonnde waЙ—oowo Й—um On, hino hattani wuurnitugol yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“aawo maayde maЙ“Й“e, fii hasbugol Й“e, yoЙ“a Й“e."
  39,43,"Kaa Й“ee sirkooЙ“e jogitor sanamuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, tefooji, Й—i Й“e jortorii nafa, hara wanaa Allah? An NulaaЙ—o, maakan Й“e: On jogitoto tefoojo, hay si tawii Й—i jeyanaa on, onon e majji, hay huunde, kadi Й—i haqqiltaa, ko wowlataa, Й—i nanataa, Й—i yi'ataa, Й—i nafataa, Й—i lorrataa?"
  39,44,"An NulaaЙ—o, maakan Й“ee sirkooЙ“e: Tefoore nden fow, ko Allah heeranii. Gooto tefataa ka Makko, si wanaa e duЕӢayee(sakkitoore) Makko. O jaЙ“antaa kadi tefoore, si wanaa mo O welanaa. Ko Kanko tun, laamagol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, woodani. Refti ko ka Makko tun, woni ruttorde mon, Г‘alnde Darngal, fii hasbeede, yoЙ“ee. O yoЙ“a kala mon, e golle mun."
  39,45,"Si fii Allah tun jantaama, Й“erЙ—e sirkooЙ“e, Й“e gomЙ—inaa laakara e ummital e hasboore e njoЙ“di Й“en, wona e tamagol. Si fii sanamuuji Й—i Й“e rewata Й—in, gaanin Allah jantaamaa, e jaka yoo, hiЙ“e wewla weltoo."
  39,46,"An NulaaЙ—o, maaku: Yaa Allah, tagirЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, no Й—i anndiranooka, AnnduЙ—o ko wirnii e ko feeГұi, Mo huunde e Й—in suuЙ—aaki. Ko An tun, Гұaawata hakkunde jeyaaЙ“e Maa Й“en, Г‘alnde Darngal, e kon ko Й“e luutondiraynoo e mun ender aduna. ЖҒannginaa goonguЙ—o e meerente, malaaЙ—o e malkisaaЙ—o."
  39,47,"Si tawno no woodannoo tooГұirЙ“e sirko e geddi Й“en, kala ko woni kon ka leydi, immorde e jawle, Й“e sottorayno Й—um, lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e Й—en Й—e yi'oyta, Й“aawo ummital maЙ“Й“e. Kono Й“e alaa feere Й—um. Hay si Й“e heЙ“u feere mun, Й“e jaЙ“anoytaake. Ontuma, feeГұirana Й“e ka Allah, noone e lepte, Й—o Й“e tijjanooki."
  39,48,"Boneeji sirku e geddi, Й—i Й“e faggitinoo Й—in feГұana Й“e, lepte Й—e Й“e jalkitaynoo Й—en huuЙ“ita Й“e, Й—en lepte Й—e Й“e hulЙ“inirtenoo, Й“e wona e jalkitugol."
  39,49,"Si Гұawu maa baasal ekn heЙ“ii neЙ—Й—o keefeero, o nadda Men, fii huncangol mo Й—um. Refti si Men okkii mo neema callal maa jawdi, o wona e wi'ugol: Anndee ko Allah okkiri lam Й—um, ko anndugol Mo, miЙ—o hanndi e mun. Kono ka goonga, Й—um ko jarrabuyee e ndaarndo; kono Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e heeferЙ“e Й“en, Й“e anndaa Й—um, Й“e mantora neema Allah on e maЙ“Й“e."
  39,50,"GomЙ—ii heeferЙ“e adinooЙ“e Й“en, wowliino ngol konngol. Kono kon ko Й“e faggitotonoo e jawle e kuЙ“eeje, duncanaano Й“e hay huunde."
  39,51,"NjoЙ“di boneeji sirku e geddi, Й—i Й“e wonunoo e faggitagil Й—in, memi Й“e. TooГұirЙ“e ko'e mun Й“en sirku e geddi, jeyaaЙ“e e Й“ee Й—oo Й“en, njoЙ“di boneeji Й—i Й“e faggitotonoo Й—in, memiroyaЙ“e, wano yawtuЙ“e Й“en. ЖҒe wonaa fuutotooЙ“e Allah, wanaa fii foolugol Mo!"
  39,52,"SirkooЙ“e Й“en wi'ay ko Й“e wi'i, hara Й“e anndaa wonnde Allah no yaГұГұana arsike on, mo O muuyani, fii jarribagol ontigi, ndaara si o yettay kaa o yedday? Ko wano non kadi O Й“iЙ—tiniranta mo O muuyani, jarribagol fahin, ontigi, ndaara si o muГұГұoto kaa o monanto eЙ“Й“oore Allah nden? Pellet, wonii e ko jantaa koo, fii yaГұГұaneede maa Й“iЙ—tinanee arsike, maandeeji, wallitirЙ—o taskagol fii Allah, wonannde yimЙ“e gomЙ—inooЙ“e. Tawde ko Й“en nafitorta Й—in maandeeji, wanaa yedduЙ“e yawtooЙ“e Й—en Aayeeje, hara hiЙ“e Й—uurnoo Й—e."
  39,53,"An NulaaЙ—o, maakan jeyaaЙ“e am yawtirЙ“e keeri Й“en sirku e geddi: wata on taЖҙo e yurmeende Allah nden, e ko O haforanta on junubaaji mon. Tawde pellet, Allah ko haforoowo junuubi Й—in fow, wonannde kala tuubanЙ—o Mo. Ko Kanko woni Haforoowo junuubi tuubayЙ“e Й“en, HinnotooЙ—o Й“e."
  39,54,"Tuubee ruttoron ka Joomi mon, golle moЖҙЖҙe, jebbilanoЙ—on Mo, ado lepte laakara Й—en arde e mon, hara on heЙ“irtaa sanamuuji Й—in wanaa yimЙ“e mon Й“en, faabo."
  39,55,"Jokkee ndee Alqur'aanaare, tawnde ko Й“urnde moЖҙЖҙude e ko Joomi mon jippinani on, haa e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, gollitiron nde, woЙ—Й—itoЙ—on e ko nde haЙ—i, ado lepte Й—en ardude on e juhal, hara on so'aa anndude, sakko hebiloron tuubugol."
  39,56,"WaЙ—ee ko yamiraЙ—on, ado wonkii wi'oyde tuma nimse nafataa janngo: Ee nimse am, e ko mi welsindii e Allah, geddi e keeferaaku. Ki tabintina wonnde ko jeyano e jalkitaynooЙ“e yimЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й—oftii Й“en."
  39,57,"Maa ki ngantinora kodduruyee, ki wi'ia: Si Allah feewnuno mi, mi jeyeteno e huluЙ“e Mo Й“en. Mi Й—oftoo yamirooje Makko, mi woЙ—Й—itoo haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko."
  39,58,"Maa ki yelora wi'ugol, nde ki yi'ata lepte Й—en: Si feere ruttagol aduna no woodannoo lam, mi tuubanayno Allah, mi jeyee e moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e golle Й“en."
  39,59,"ЖҠum gasatira no faaliraЙ—aa non feewirde ! Tawde Aayeeje Amen Й—en aruno e maaЙ—a, fennuЙ—aa Й—e, mawnintiniЙ—aa, laatiЙ—aa jeyaaЙ—o e yedduЙ“e Allah Й“en, yeddi Aayeeje Makko Й—en e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en."
  39,60,"Г‘alnde Darngal, a yi'oyay fenunooЙ“e e hoore Allah Й“en, Й“e dammbi sirku e Й“iЙ—Й—o e Makko, hiЙ“e Й“awli geece, hakkee ko Й“e malkisaa. Wonaa ka Jahannama woni jaaЖҙorde mawnintinaniiЙ“e gomЙ—ingol Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko on? Ko ton tigiri, woni weerde maЙ“Й“e."
  39,61,"Allah hisinira huluЙ“e Mo Й—oftii haЙ—itii Й“en, e lepte, O naadaugol Й“e ka maloore Aljanna. Bone lepte memataa Й“en, wanaa kamЙ“e woni ko sunoytoo, fii ko feЖҙЖҙi e geЙ“oy aduna."
  39,62,"Ko Allah woni TaguЙ—o kala huunde, wanaa goЙ—Й—o goЙ—Й—um goo. Ko Kanko kadi woni FawtiiЙ—o kala huunde, O Toppitoo fii mayre, O waЙ—ira nde, no O haajiri."
  39,63,"Ko Kanko tun, jogitii ngaluuji moЖҙЖҙere Й—in, ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Himo yeЙ—a Й—i Mo O haajani, O Й—awa Й—i Mo O muuyi. YedduЙ“e Aayeeje Allah Й“en non, ko Й“en woni hayruЙ“e Й“en. Tawde Й“e faЙ—ii gomЙ—ingol e nguurndam maЙ“Й“e Й—am aduna, e hoore Й“e naatoyay Й“e heddoo ka Yiite, laakara."
  39,64,"An NulaaЙ—o, maakan Й“ee sirkooЙ“e jokkuЙ“e maa, fii rewugol sanamuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in: E on yamiray lam, onon Й“ee majjuЙ“e fii Joomi mun, nde mi rewata ko woori Allah? Anndee ko Allah tun, hanndi e reweede, mi rewataa, si wanaa Kanko."
  39,65,"GomЙ—ii Allah wahayinii maaЙ—a, an NulaaЙ—o, O wahayini kadi e NulaaЙ“e adinooЙ“e ma Й“en: si a kafidii e Allah goЙ—Й—um goo, ko pellet, golle maa moЖҙЖҙe Й—en bonay; jeyeЙ—aa e hayruЙ“e aduna Й“en, sabu hayruЙ“e diina maa, hayroyaa kadi e lepte laakara Й—en."
  39,66,"Ko Allah tun, si a reway, hara a kafidaali Mo e goЙ—Й—um goo, jeyeЙ—aa e yettooЙ“e Mo neemajji Й—i O neemini e maaЙ—a Й—in."
  39,67,"SirkooЙ“e Й“en mawniniraali Allah, no O haaniri mawninireede, tuma Й“e kafidunoo Mo e taguuji Makko lo'uЙ—i, Й“e yejjiti wonnde no jeyaa e kattane Makko ngal, tawde leydi ndin e ko woni mayri kon : immorde e pelle e leЙ—Й—e e canЙ—i e boyli, fow e mun, Г‘alnde Darngal, ko e tamannde Makko wonata, kammuuli Й—in jeeЙ—iЙ—i kadi, fow majji taggiree Гұaamo Makko ngon. Senayee woodanii Mo ! O laaЙ“ii O toowii kon ko sirkooЙ“e Й“en fiЙ“ata wowla e Makko."
  39,68,"Г‘alnde Malaa'ikaajo on wuttoyta ka Allaandu, kala ko woni ko kammuuli e ka leydi fow maayay, refti wuttee e mayru Й—iЙ—aЙ“ol, fii ummital, tawaa Й“e fow Й“e wuurnitaama, hiЙ“e darii habbii ko Allah waЙ—ata Й“e."
  39,69,"Leydi ndin jalbirora, tuma JeyЙ—o ndi On feeГұiroyta Гұaawugol hakkunde jeyaaЙ“e Й“en. Talki golle Й—in sennditee, AnnbaaЙ“e Й“en addee, mofte Muhammadu (jom kisiyee Й—en) Й“adine, fii seeditanagol Й“eya AnnabaaЙ“e, e yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en. Allah Гұaawira nunЙ—al hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, wonaa Й“e tooГұeteeЙ“e nden Г‘alnde: goЙ—Й—o Й“eydantaake bonЙ—i, o Й—uytantaake moЖҙЖҙi."
  39,70,"Allah yoЙ“ita wonki kala, ko ki golli kon, woni bone maa moЖҙЖҙere. Ko Kanko Allah Й“uri anndude ko Й“e gollata kon. Huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, woni bonЙ—e maa moЖҙЖҙe. O yoЙ“itoyay Й“e Й—um, nden Г‘alnde."
  39,71,"Malaa'ika'en soggiroya yeddunooЙ“e Allah Й“en, ka Jahannama, dente-dente, hoynaaЙ“e. Si Й“e hewtii nge, dame magge udditaneeЙ“e, Malaa'ika ayninaaЙ“e nge Й“en jaЙ“Й“ora Й“e feloore wi'ugol: Enee, NulaaЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e mooЙ—on, hewtaano on, Й“e no jannganaynoo on Aayeeje Allah, jippinaaЙ—e e mon Й—en, Й“e rentinira on, hawrugol e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e Г‘alnde Darngal? ЖҒe qirritora wi'ugol: Ko non woniri, ko woni tun, hari Konngol lepte ngol jojjiino e yedduЙ“e Й“en. Menen non, ko men yeddunooЙ“e."
  39,72,"ЖҒe wi'iranee hoyneede, e teЖҙagol yurmeende Allah e yaltugol ka Yiite ton: naatiree dame Jahannama ngen, lutton ton poomaa. Nge bonii weerde mawnintiniiЙ“e toownitanii goonga Й“en."
  39,73,"Malaa'ika'en Й—owira muumini'en, hulunooЙ“e Joomi mun, Й—oftinooЙ“e yamaruyeeji Makko, Й“e woЙ—Й—itii e haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko, teddungal, haa ka Aljannaaji, hara ko dente-dente. Si wonii Й“e hewtii ton, dame majji udditanaama Й“e, Malaa'ikaaЙ“e ayninaaЙ“e ton Й“e wi'ana Й“e: on hisii e kala lorra, maa ko huloton. ЖҒerЙ—e mon e golle mon laaЙ“ii. Naatiree Alajanna on, duumagol ton poomaa."
  39,74,"Muumini'en si naadaama Aljanna, Й“e wi'a: Yettoore woodanii Allah, laatinanЙ—o men fodoore Makko, e Й—emЙ—e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, wonnde O naadoyay men Aljanna. O ronini men leydi Aljanna ndin, meЙ—en hoЙ—ira e mayri, kala ka men yiЙ—i. Mbarjaari gollunooЙ“e golle moЖҙЖҙe Й“en, fii Allah, ndi moЖҙЖҙii barjaari."
  39,75,"Nden Г‘alnde, a yi'ay Malaa'ika'en no fiiltii Arsi ki, hiЙ“e senina yettugol Joomi maЙ“Й“e, e huunde ko heeferЙ“e wi'ata Mo, kon ko haananaa Mo. Allah Гұaawira nunЙ—al, hakkunde tageefo ngon fow: O teddina Mo muuyanaaЙ“e Й“en, O lepte lepteeЙ“e Й“en. Ontuma wi'ee: Yettoore woodanii Allah, JeyЙ—o tageefo ngon, e fii ko O Гұaawiri kon yurmeende, hakkunde jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, O heertinani yurmeende Makko nden, muumini'en, yedduЙ“e Й“en hanndi e lepte Й—en."
